{"tid":2244722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"и”ЎиӢұж–ҮпјҡжңҖиҝ‘жҲ‘зҡ„жҺЁзү№е’ҢIGдёҠеҮәзҸҫиЁұеӨҡеҚ°еәҰз¶ІеҸӢ^_^","createTime":"2020-10-15T16:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T04:06:02.000Z","uid":226955,"like":190,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a5388c7aa10a42297beb9aa70001120d3d3bab10","tid":2244722,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"жңҖиҝ‘жҲ‘зҡ„жҺЁзү№е’ҢIGдёҠеҮәзҸҫиЁұеӨҡеҚ°еәҰз¶ІеҸӢпјҢжҲ‘еҫҲй«ҳиҲҲиғҪд»ЈиЎЁеҸ°зҒЈе’ҢеӨ§е®¶жү“жӢӣе‘јпјҒ<br />\nгҖҖгҖҖ<br />\n#NamasteрҹҷҸto our friends from #India рҹҮ®рҹҮі! Thank you for following me here. Your warm regards remind me of fond memories from time spent in your incredible country, your architectural marvels, vibrant culture &amp; kind people are truly unforgettable. I miss my time there dearly. <br />\nгҖҖгҖҖ<br />\nNamasteпјҲйҖҷжҳҜHindiе•ҸеҖҷиӘһпјүпјҒдҫҶиҮӘеҚ°еәҰзҡ„жңӢеҸӢеҖ‘пјҢеӨ§е®¶еҘҪпјҒи¬қи¬қеӨ§е®¶й—ңжіЁжҲ‘гҖӮ дҪ еҖ‘жә«жҡ–зҡ„е•ҸеҖҷпјҢеӢҫиө·жҲ‘еңЁеҚ°еәҰйҖҷеҖӢдёҚеҸҜжҖқиӯ°зҡ„еңӢе®¶жүҖз•ҷдёӢзҡ„зҫҺеҘҪеӣһжҶ¶гҖӮ дҪ еҖ‘д»Өдәәй©ҡиү·зҡ„е»әзҜүгҖҒз”ҹж©ҹи“¬еӢғзҡ„ж–ҮеҢ–е’ҢиҰӘеҲҮе–„иүҜзҡ„дәәж°‘пјҢйғҪи®“жҲ‘йӣЈд»ҘеҝҳжҮ·гҖӮ жҲ‘зңҹеҝғжғіеҝөжҲ‘еңЁеҚ°еәҰзҡ„жҷӮе…үгҖӮ<br />\nгҖҖгҖҖ<br />\nвһЎпёҸдҫҶжҲ‘зҡ„TwitterзңӢжӣҙеӨҡпјҡ<a href=\"https://twitter.com/iingwen/status/1315966767567495170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiingwen%2Fstatus%2F1315966767567495170&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=0641ab2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiingwen%2Fstatus%2F1315966767567495170&h=cc6cbb6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/iingwen/status/1315966767567495170</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RKGYsO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RKGYsO.jpg&h=66f7f121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3O4Weu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3O4Weu.jpg&h=f78985d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7e36fa981d424d0fb0fc60b98a1f4a34221abe8","tid":2244722,"uid":226955,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"д»ҠеӨ©зҡ„е®өеӨңж–ҮпјҢжҳҜдҫҶиҮӘеҚ°еәҰзҡ„зҫҺйЈҹж–ҷзҗҶпјҒеҘҪеӨҡз¶ІеҸӢеңЁжҺЁзү№дёҠи·ҹжҲ‘еҲҶдә«пјҢдҪ д№ҹжңүжҺЁи–Ұзҡ„е—Һпјҹ<br />\nгҖҖгҖҖ<br />\n#Taiwan is lucky to be home to many Indian restaurants, &amp; Taiwanese people love them. I always go for chana masala and naan, while #chai always takes me back to my travels in #India, and memories of a vibrant, diverse &amp; colourful country. What are your favourite Indian dishes?<br />\nгҖҖгҖҖ<br />\nеӨ§е®¶жңҖе–ңжӯЎд»ҖйәјеҚ°еәҰж–ҷзҗҶе‘ўпјҹз•ҷиЁҖе‘ҠиЁҙжҲ‘гҖҒд№ҹе‘ҠиЁҙеҚ°еәҰзҡ„жңӢеҸӢеҗ§пјҒ<br />\nгҖҖгҖҖ<br />\nрҹ‘үжӣҙеӨҡиӢұж–ҮжҺЁж–Үи«ӢзңӢжҲ‘зҡ„Twitterпјҡ<a href=\"https://twitter.com/iingwen/status/1316608930651402240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiingwen%2Fstatus%2F1316608930651402240&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=a3297515\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiingwen%2Fstatus%2F1316608930651402240&h=f2ee4124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/iingwen/status/1316608930651402240</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5rS1Ys5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rS1Ys5.jpg&h=43604465&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ece48c3864ccab22c7b273d029352ff2675505a6","tid":2244722,"uid":226955,"like":149,"dislike":0,"score":149,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nn197mC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNn197mC.jpg&h=7733f509&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8456dceacb6e82b25f9f17025ffdf04a607730d2","tid":2244722,"uid":201751,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"еӨ§зёҪзөұ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=